Minimal OpenCL GLFW OpenGL 4 example based on:

Adventures in OpenCL
http://enja.org
https://github.com/enjalot/adventures_in_opencl

We demonstrate OpenCL and OpenGL context sharing by making a simple particle system.

Build:
make a build directory and build the tutorial
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make

execute the example program
./minimal-opencl-gl4

Dependencies:
* OpenCL
* OpenGL
* GLEW
* GLFW3
